{"h9b4774c0g2900g4a64gbf79g81016f3685b2": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "94d9e4b1-29d1-84cd-4421-192c9541204f"], "hdccd613fg0b58g46f9g8693g80923533aebf": ["<i>You...</i>", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "39b4260e-9d08-c608-e4f4-1a7cd7d95c64"], "hadf3a015g5654g486aga3f0gcd8204b7da74": ["*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "62ea3e80-d633-f1d7-7cf9-21cc4537b0f6"], "h74074537g9e14g4250gaf7eg680fff893380": ["Who are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "683accf3-929d-a988-d756-6c2518b86919"], "h887835b9gdfb2g49c7gb438g316160a90fd1": ["Zevlor... Hellrider... but <i>cast out...</i>", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "bc620af3-8639-e008-e8b3-55b0223454f7"], "h7cc0b85cg65ffg4f03g8e24g8e988d45afbb": ["What should the tieflings do now you're dead?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "750391ed-a0d2-03eb-53c6-302f04ba92b0"], "hf1e81a41g9c48g4893gaa6ege3b2cbfb03a9": ["Finish... the plan. Go... where... they belong...", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "a3dc4633-5479-2a08-9662-bd92222c2fa6"], "h3f7b5bb9g5344g4129gba93gc2cb1bf54b04": ["Did you have any secrets?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "37303e66-f4ec-f2bd-a269-320594c3a941"], "h5eeb2d2dgaf66g4af9g9e78gec32c5f0c6c7": ["I would have... sacrificed... them <i>all... </i>for the Absolute.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "f88e553e-2521-c510-8cac-015c6a4fa265"], "h86b364bcg503dg4541gac34g038a0224beda": ["Plenty... to have... none... to tell...", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "6d07fbec-eb8c-7fa9-85bd-33086de9ed5f"], "hb1e2ddfcga31cg4417gb984g735dcfcc0584": ["You followed the Absolute - why?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "14bba40a-a924-60c3-b05c-7a02a44227e3"], "h9b563978g0369g4919gb10fg1f69d5638e8f": ["I heard tell... whispers... a new power... could raise up those who had been cast out...", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "6e20f03d-2e92-8bc7-0530-9f54733120bf"], "h6380fd60g48b5g49d5g99e9g5552847224f1": ["Sick... of being... cast out...", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "fb7d3eb0-4370-5e83-7aca-da5ba888cc17"], "h30e116d0g0afeg4fd9gaf9eg5e7e27e82a83": ["Where are you from?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "192b2a87-8bfa-5f1d-e7c4-0d604abbaae3"], "hc09e5b77gfae2g403bg9407g3e88a04d75ca": ["Elturel... city on the river... terrible times...", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "c1518b1b-c374-5dd9-9a07-e9f2f64c2cd4"], "h6fa87e19g0097g43c2g9640g5329af8c3f0f": ["What happened in Elturel?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "b6ca7419-02a0-99d0-e239-2e2e2e7528fc"], "hf3131141g5d00g4e1agbb8ag4bbd0a6b6d52": ["Dragged... to the Hells. They blamed... us.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "e5929e74-71d8-81ef-2c74-1da68718eb40"], "h9f09de05gb082g40b3g9c65g5da10348d181": ["Fools.", "475200ee-cc3c-4dbe-84b1-1820c02ea26a", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "34fca951-7157-68b1-c1b2-fe0f97bad036"], "h846ff166g8150g4d90g8bdeg82b029af4ec4": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "8c0e0550-7369-d40d-d27e-e597e3bcd2b0"], "hf7b628b2gccdeg4a62gb0a1g3df3b1b86e18": ["*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_General_Dead_TieflingLeader.html", "d0975367-ebc0-6de2-0857-553d1cbf3746"]}